  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A requirement binds experimental-validation as the required verification method; however, the supporting validation activity was conducted as a literature-review of published hemolysis datasets, which the narrative presents as complementary evidence sufficient to satisfy the requirement. The structured activity type disagrees with the requirement's required method.",
